      {
        "category": "summary",
        "text": "An update is available for vulkan-validation-layers, vulkan-headers, vulkan-tools, spirv-tools, vulkan-loader.\nThis update affects Rocky Linux 8.\nA Common Vulnerability Scoring System (CVSS) base score, which gives a detailed severity rating, is available for each vulnerability from the CVE list",
