      {
        "category": "description",
        "text": "Vulkan validation layers\n\nBug Fix(es) and Enhancement(s):\n\n* [8.10.z] Vulkan rebase (z-stream): glslang (JIRA:Rocky Linux-54282)\n\n* [8.10.z] Vulkan rebase (z-stream): spirv-headers (JIRA:Rocky Linux-54284)\n\n* [8.10.z] Vulkan rebase (z-stream): spirv-tools (JIRA:Rocky Linux-54285)\n\n* [8.10.z] Vulkan rebase (z-stream): vulkan-headers (JIRA:Rocky Linux-54286)\n\n* [8.10.z] Vulkan rebase (z-stream): vulkan-loader (JIRA:Rocky Linux-54287)\n\n* [8.10.z] Vulkan rebase (z-stream): vulkan-tools (JIRA:Rocky Linux-54288)\n\n* [8.10.z] Vulkan rebase (z-stream): vulkan-validation-layers (JIRA:Rocky Linux-54290)\n\nThis advisory is provided by Ctrl IQ, Inc for Rocky Linux systems. For more information about CIQ security practices, visit https://ciq.com/security.",
